data.title: Because times are changing.
data.meta_description: Discover Argos Watches, where vintage charm meets Horology. Our collection boasts exquisite timepieces. featuring authentic mechanical movements. We proudly stand among the select few companies in India offering vintage-style watches. This store is for our beloved Indian Customers
data.text:
Fell in love with the watch as soon as I saw it online and immediately purchased it. It wasn't available and was made to order. The argos team took 45 days to deliver it. Expectations were high and I must say the watch hasn't disappointed. Reliable movement, beautiful dial design and an excellent Jubilee strap design. The only downside for the watch is that it's 50m water resist which I wish could have been 100m to make it an even more versatile watch. But otherwise a wonderful addition to my collection and I'm looking forward to many more Argos innovations in the future

Beautiful watch

Worth every penny

Olive green dial , Streep strap cannot be ignored on your wrists

I went to Kamal watch company to get few straps removed to fit my wrists . Watch service said all the features of very high watches like omega have been used .

Goes well with formals and Casuals .

I am a basically a watch maker and collection of watches. I found this watch has a beautiful look and time keeping also excellant (+ 5 sec per day) . My only contention is it shouls have a date window at 3 oclock position and size should small preferably 38 mm or lower. I will give 9 out of 10 marks. The company is not sticking to committed delivery as I received the watch after 10 delayed days of committed delivery.

Loved the watch when I first saw, love the wait for it to arrive and loving it when I proudly wear on my wrist. The watch is beautiful and straps are so well designed.

Always wanted to buy a automatic watch but stopped everytime because of the high price but after seeing the ad and the pricing didn’t even hesitate and without wasting any minute I placed the order and I am loving it 🥰
